<P>II am not a rampaging psycho pk I have only killed 2 people, both tried to pk me first.

<P>The point of my Previous post was that i think its dumb that A loot of these rules are OOC themselves.
<BR>An example of a in-game rule would be in Meridian if you were strong and you pked a newbie you would get a reverant (spirit of person you kill) that would come and attack you and hunt you down relentlessly for revenge now although that idea is a little lame it at east stays in the fanstasy game spirit that is what I am talking about instead of a -/+ 4 level limit they shuld think of something else more creative, not just a invisbile wall that protects people from you, or you from them. It distaches the roleplaying aspect a bit from the game. Thats what I meant
<P>HolyDevil
<P>Also will CC members have the CC in the names? or in their bio? how can I find out if someone is CC?
